{"tid":609691,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[IPO]HKE Holdings(01726)孖展增超購近１倍","createTime":"2018-03-29T08:44:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-06T08:23:30.000Z","uid":74411,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c9cdba731502056ed947c23896171affa72416b5","tid":609691,"uid":74411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:44:18.000Z","msg":"【ＩＰＯ反應】消息指，ＨＫＥ（０１７２６）孖展增超購近１倍<br />\n<br />\n　　《經濟通通訊社２９日專訊》以新加坡為基地的醫療保健行業專業承建商ＨＫＥ　<br />\nＨｏｌｄｉｎｇｓ（０１７２６）昨日（２８日）首日招股，孖展錄得２１８０萬元，較<br />\n１１００萬元公開集資額超額認購近１倍。<br />\n　　該股按每股０﹒４５至０﹒５５元發售２億股，９０％作配售股份，１０％作公開發售，集<br />\n資規模９０００萬至１﹒１億元。以每手５０００股計算，入場費為２７７７﹒７１元。<br />\n　　ＨＫＥ將自昨日起至下周三（４日）中午招股，４月４日定價，４月１８日主板掛牌。保薦<br />\n人為德健融資。若按中間價每股０﹒５元計算，集資淨額約７４００萬元。<br />\n<br />\n抽唔抽好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f0b5c8100b518f38b4c8d97048b7a7748db40f","tid":609691,"uid":74411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T08:52:07.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04e7e9902c13d081fe5916f80f69081aea23a6f0","tid":609691,"uid":22757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T09:09:53.000Z","msg":"抽！"},{"pid":"d8fc5dd567bca7606631304b216691a03b672ba4","tid":609691,"uid":74411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T09:38:36.000Z","msg":"今第二日招股,孖展錄得逾51倍超購。"},{"pid":"8717fe005a06e6c90074b0e89904394950cc85bc","tid":609691,"uid":18764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T11:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b9f7e0d14d55662bde09fda48d2e4baf4f221d1","tid":609691,"uid":51920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-29T15:40:00.000Z","msg":"又有音樂椅玩"},{"pid":"d6c2e837ddbf2f949b41fc90cbc5d7c59b7c1106","tid":609691,"uid":74411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"9b9f7e